events: It is strange, you will never change it, my range is unlimited.
Your moveset outdated, success is prohibited.
Try to match my speed, having trouble keeping pace?
You're slow, fell behing, in the race, last place.
You're stuck in the past, you will never last.
Take off the mask, imitating the glory of the fastest thing alive.
Skills in decline, flawed by design, stuck in rewind.
Running through your mind, running throigh your head, I'm ahead.
Made of lead, I'm not playing games, making real threats.
Face it, you're out of time, out of line.
Dead or alive, you will be mine.
